from Madura in Southern 
<collectingCountry box="[815,876,620,644]" name="India" pageId="6" pageNumber="494">India</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,151,788]" pageId="6" pageNumber="494">
Although the different general habitus and several characters mentioned in the diagnosis not shared by 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Aradidae" genus="Signocoris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kaszabi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="494">S. kaszabi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, these might be sufficient for the erection of a new genus for 
<taxonomicName box="[927,1064,692,716]" class="Insecta" family="Aradidae" genus="Signocoris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nilgiricus">
<emphasis box="[927,1064,692,716]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="494">S. nilgiricus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
n.sp.. We refrain here to propose this new genus, and assign the new species tentatively to 
<emphasis box="[847,967,728,751]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="494">Signocoris</emphasis>
until more specimens are available for comparative studies.
</paragraph>
